WEBVTT

00:01:54.960 --> 00:01:55.800
What the heck?

00:02:08.199 --> 00:02:09.400
Are you praying here?

00:02:09.560 --> 00:02:10.289
Does it work?

00:02:15.400 --> 00:02:15.960
No rush.

00:02:16.000 --> 00:02:17.040
Keep holding your breath.

00:02:17.040 --> 00:02:18.170
We have time to wait.

00:02:39.720 --> 00:02:40.850
Forty-two seconds.

00:02:41.400 --> 00:02:42.000
Liu Jiang,

00:02:42.240 --> 00:02:43.440
your lung capacity is terrible.

00:02:43.440 --> 00:02:44.000
Oh, my God.

00:02:44.000 --> 00:02:45.000
Wait, you scared me to death.

00:02:45.000 --> 00:02:46.200
Where am I?

00:02:47.079 --> 00:02:47.440
Hey.

00:02:48.160 --> 00:02:48.820
Who are you?

00:02:50.960 --> 00:02:51.440
Hey,

00:02:52.120 --> 00:02:53.240
you're quite handsome.

00:02:53.240 --> 00:02:54.280
You look like an actor.

00:02:54.280 --> 00:02:54.720
Thank you.

00:02:54.720 --> 00:02:55.320
You too.

00:02:55.560 --> 00:02:56.240
Why are you running?

00:02:56.240 --> 00:02:56.600
Hey.

00:02:56.640 --> 00:02:58.079
What's wrong with running?

00:02:58.079 --> 00:02:59.120
Running is my right.

00:02:59.120 --> 00:03:00.200
Running is my freedom.

00:03:00.200 --> 00:03:01.240
I jog every day.

00:03:01.240 --> 00:03:02.640
What's wrong with exercising?

00:03:02.640 --> 00:03:03.800
Can't I just have some fun?

00:03:03.800 --> 00:03:05.240
Having fun in a pile of dead bodies?

00:03:05.240 --> 00:03:06.200
You two have a problem.

00:03:06.200 --> 00:03:07.320
Looking down on the dead?

00:03:07.320 --> 00:03:09.360
Let me educate you today.

00:03:09.600 --> 00:03:10.440
Everyone dies someday,

00:03:10.440 --> 00:03:11.280
either as heavy as Mount Tai

00:03:11.280 --> 00:03:12.320
or as light as a feather.

00:03:12.320 --> 00:03:12.920
You know?

00:03:13.080 --> 00:03:14.560
Your values are problematic.

00:03:14.560 --> 00:03:15.920
Don't look down on the dead.

00:03:15.920 --> 00:03:17.280
Without life, there is no...

00:03:17.280 --> 00:03:18.140
First Brigade,

00:03:18.680 --> 00:03:19.520
Major Crimes.

00:03:28.600 --> 00:03:29.640
Sun,

00:03:31.680 --> 00:03:32.240
Gou...

00:03:34.760 --> 00:03:35.520
Uh, Sun Ri...

00:03:36.079 --> 00:03:36.960
Sun Ju...

00:03:37.880 --> 00:03:40.410
You're a doctor with this level of education?

00:03:43.040 --> 00:03:43.640
Cuff him.

00:04:10.960 --> 00:04:12.760
This kid is pretty dedicated.

00:04:12.920 --> 00:04:15.120
According to the information we have, yes.

00:04:15.120 --> 00:04:16.560
Did you find Liu Jiang's wife?

00:04:16.560 --> 00:04:17.360
We brought her back.

00:04:17.360 --> 00:04:18.800
Xiaohan and I will go question her now.

00:04:18.800 --> 00:04:19.200
Okay.

00:04:23.600 --> 00:04:26.330
It's so hot, and you won't even pour me some water.

00:04:28.480 --> 00:04:30.410
The... The air pressure is too low.

00:04:31.240 --> 00:04:33.640
It's so hot. Can you pour me a glass of water?

00:04:34.560 --> 00:04:35.760
What the hell is this?

00:04:41.040 --> 00:04:43.240
You know why we brought you here, right?

00:04:43.680 --> 00:04:44.480
I have no idea.

00:04:46.880 --> 00:04:47.440
No rush.

00:04:47.480 --> 00:04:48.280
Take your time.

00:04:48.280 --> 00:04:48.680
Ah.

00:04:57.880 --> 00:04:58.320
No,

00:04:59.520 --> 00:05:00.320
Officers,

00:05:01.240 --> 00:05:02.720
I just sold some medicine.

00:05:02.840 --> 00:05:05.360
There's no need for such a big scene to bring me in,

00:05:05.360 --> 00:05:05.680
is there?

00:05:05.680 --> 00:05:07.400
You think it's as simple

00:05:07.400 --> 00:05:09.160
as just prescribing some medicine?

00:05:09.160 --> 00:05:09.600
No.

00:05:10.160 --> 00:05:11.600
What's wrong with me selling some medicine?

00:05:11.600 --> 00:05:12.520
I heal the wounded

00:05:12.520 --> 00:05:13.480
and help others.

00:05:13.720 --> 00:05:15.080
If that counts as healing the wounded,

00:05:15.080 --> 00:05:16.480
then I'm the God of Medicine reincarnated.

00:05:16.480 --> 00:05:17.480
That's not right.

00:05:18.120 --> 00:05:19.580
Officers, let me tell you,

00:05:19.760 --> 00:05:20.960
since I got out, don't I have to

00:05:20.960 --> 00:05:21.600
survive?

00:05:21.840 --> 00:05:23.000
Don't I have to support my family,

00:05:23.000 --> 00:05:24.660
and feed my wife and daughter?

00:05:24.880 --> 00:05:26.280
Are you two going to support me?

00:05:26.280 --> 00:05:27.680
Then I have to find a job.

00:05:27.880 --> 00:05:29.360
Let me make it clear to you first.

00:05:29.360 --> 00:05:29.880
I...

00:05:30.200 --> 00:05:31.200
My prescriptions

00:05:31.200 --> 00:05:32.560
are all in the medical books.

00:05:32.560 --> 00:05:33.890
And the medicine I sold,

00:05:34.680 --> 00:05:35.240
well,

00:05:35.240 --> 00:05:36.240
isn't fake.

00:05:36.440 --> 00:05:38.880
It was prescribed by a legitimate Chinese pharmacy.

00:05:38.880 --> 00:05:39.320
Legi-

00:05:39.360 --> 00:05:41.240
Stop messing around, you hear me?

00:05:41.600 --> 00:05:43.730
If there's no problem, why did you run?

00:05:44.000 --> 00:05:44.400
I...

00:05:45.159 --> 00:05:45.840
Liu Jiang.

00:05:47.320 --> 00:05:48.840
Since May 17,

00:05:49.680 --> 00:05:50.810
where have you been?

00:05:51.440 --> 00:05:53.080
Officer, forget about May 7.

00:05:53.200 --> 00:05:53.840
As for me.

00:05:53.840 --> 00:05:54.800
On the 17th.

00:05:56.159 --> 00:05:57.400
Right, the 17th.

00:05:57.400 --> 00:05:58.330
The 17th, right.

00:05:58.880 --> 00:05:59.440
As for me,

00:05:59.440 --> 00:06:00.840
all 365 days are the same.

00:06:01.120 --> 00:06:01.880
I work during the day,

00:06:01.880 --> 00:06:03.240
from 7 a.m. to 8 p.m., rain or shine.

00:06:03.240 --> 00:06:05.320
I go to work at the hospital on time every morning.

00:06:05.320 --> 00:06:06.360
After work, I go straight home.

00:06:06.360 --> 00:06:07.440
I don't go anywhere else.

00:06:07.440 --> 00:06:07.970
Alright.

00:06:08.560 --> 00:06:09.280
Hurry up,

00:06:09.280 --> 00:06:09.840
officer.

00:06:09.840 --> 00:06:10.560
It's time.

00:06:10.640 --> 00:06:12.840
I need to go back and be with my daughter.

00:06:12.920 --> 00:06:13.760
Hurry up.

00:06:14.080 --> 00:06:15.360
He came back at 8 p.m.

00:06:15.560 --> 00:06:16.440
On his way back,

00:06:16.440 --> 00:06:18.160
he usually buys a toy for the kid.

00:06:18.160 --> 00:06:19.560
Oh, he buys one every day.

00:06:19.560 --> 00:06:21.000
There's barely any room for them at home.

00:06:21.000 --> 00:06:21.640
But,

00:06:21.920 --> 00:06:23.000
that's his only good trait.

00:06:23.000 --> 00:06:23.930
He loves the kid.

00:06:25.400 --> 00:06:26.120
Around

00:06:27.480 --> 00:06:28.440
or 8:30,

00:06:28.440 --> 00:06:29.370
he would be home.

00:06:30.160 --> 00:06:31.240
After dinner,

00:06:31.560 --> 00:06:33.840
he played with the kid for a while and went to bed.

00:06:33.840 --> 00:06:34.600
He slept until

00:06:34.600 --> 00:06:36.530
he woke up at 6:00 the next morning.

00:06:37.159 --> 00:06:38.159
He had breakfast,

00:06:38.240 --> 00:06:39.000
got ready,

00:06:39.040 --> 00:06:39.970
and went to work.

00:06:41.920 --> 00:06:43.280
His time at home at night

00:06:43.640 --> 00:06:45.040
can only be proven by you.

00:06:45.120 --> 00:06:46.120
Not necessarily.

00:06:46.600 --> 00:06:48.080
We have a security camera at home.

00:06:48.080 --> 00:06:49.480
Does that count as proof?

00:06:51.040 --> 00:06:52.570
You have a security camera?

00:06:52.960 --> 00:06:53.800
Yeah.

00:06:53.840 --> 00:06:55.040
This thing is quite expensive.

00:06:55.040 --> 00:06:56.360
My husband installed it.

00:06:56.360 --> 00:06:57.120
He said it's

00:06:57.360 --> 00:06:59.159
to scare those debt collectors.

00:06:59.200 --> 00:07:00.360
If they dare to mess around,

00:07:00.360 --> 00:07:01.360
we can take the video

00:07:01.360 --> 00:07:02.440
to the police station to sue them

00:07:02.440 --> 00:07:04.170
and let the police arrest them.

00:07:04.200 --> 00:07:04.880
Qiao Sisi.

00:07:05.440 --> 00:07:06.300
Do you know her?

00:07:06.320 --> 00:07:07.650
Also known as Qiaoqiao.

00:07:08.160 --> 00:07:09.090
I don't know her.

00:07:11.040 --> 00:07:11.840
What about this one?

00:07:11.840 --> 00:07:12.520
Kong Jiao.

00:07:15.600 --> 00:07:16.530
I don't know her.

00:07:24.520 --> 00:07:24.960
No.

00:07:25.000 --> 00:07:26.560
You must know this one.

00:07:26.840 --> 00:07:27.500
Zhang Biao.

00:07:31.480 --> 00:07:32.320
You all know.

00:07:32.480 --> 00:07:33.520
Isn't this

00:07:34.159 --> 00:07:35.600
Abiao from Huguang?

00:07:36.400 --> 00:07:37.120
I know him.

00:07:37.120 --> 00:07:38.080
But we're not close.

00:07:38.080 --> 00:07:38.680
Not close.

00:07:41.400 --> 00:07:43.000
Then what about this person?

00:07:43.440 --> 00:07:44.240
Hao Quezi.

00:07:44.520 --> 00:07:45.780
Do you know Hao Weiguo?

00:07:47.760 --> 00:07:48.960
Still don't know him?

00:07:53.000 --> 00:07:54.240
Let me remind you.

00:07:55.159 --> 00:07:56.120
Last year,

00:07:56.800 --> 00:07:57.960
you gave him

00:07:58.080 --> 00:07:59.440
a large sum of money.

00:08:05.520 --> 00:08:06.200
I remember now.

00:08:06.200 --> 00:08:07.280
I know him.

00:08:07.960 --> 00:08:09.920
Doesn't he run a money-lending business?

00:08:09.920 --> 00:08:11.120
I just gave him some money

00:08:11.120 --> 00:08:12.320
to earn some interest.

00:08:12.320 --> 00:08:12.760
Right?

00:08:13.000 --> 00:08:14.280
His company is legit.

00:08:14.360 --> 00:08:15.360
They have a license.

00:08:15.360 --> 00:08:16.040
Officers,

00:08:16.520 --> 00:08:17.800
there's nothing wrong with me doing that, right?

00:08:17.800 --> 00:08:19.160
You're really something.

00:08:19.160 --> 00:08:20.440
You're up to your neck in debt,

00:08:20.440 --> 00:08:21.840
but you won't pay it back.

00:08:22.280 --> 00:08:23.000
Instead, you go

00:08:23.000 --> 00:08:24.560
to that Cripple Hao to help you

00:08:24.560 --> 00:08:25.420
earn interest.

00:08:26.040 --> 00:08:27.840
I can tell you two have no experience.

00:08:27.840 --> 00:08:29.640
You've lived too comfortably.

00:08:30.360 --> 00:08:31.120
Officers,

00:08:31.680 --> 00:08:33.280
you can't pay back borrowed money.

00:08:33.280 --> 00:08:34.799
Not even a single cent.

00:08:34.880 --> 00:08:35.679
When it comes to paying back money,

00:08:35.679 --> 00:08:37.440
if you pay it back once, there will be a second time.

00:08:37.440 --> 00:08:39.240
And these guys chase me every day.

00:08:39.240 --> 00:08:39.840
Let me tell you,

00:08:39.840 --> 00:08:40.799
these bastards

00:08:40.799 --> 00:08:42.400
will definitely kill me.

00:08:42.400 --> 00:08:43.659
Just thinking about it

00:08:44.200 --> 00:08:45.200
makes me furious.

00:08:52.080 --> 00:08:53.140
What are you doing?

00:08:55.520 --> 00:08:56.320
Look closely.

00:08:57.200 --> 00:08:58.000
Look clearly.

00:09:01.920 --> 00:09:02.480
Who is it?

00:09:03.640 --> 00:09:04.640
Qiao Sisi.

00:09:04.920 --> 00:09:05.720
Kong Jiao,

00:09:06.240 --> 00:09:07.200
found murdered

00:09:07.400 --> 00:09:08.360
on May 17.

00:09:08.920 --> 00:09:09.680
Zhang Biao,

00:09:10.440 --> 00:09:11.700
killed in an explosion

00:09:11.880 --> 00:09:12.640
on May 19.

00:09:13.120 --> 00:09:14.040
Wang Hongjia,

00:09:14.760 --> 00:09:15.800
severely injured

00:09:16.360 --> 00:09:17.080
on May 27.

00:09:17.960 --> 00:09:18.490
This one,

00:09:19.480 --> 00:09:21.410
Hao Weiguo, whom you gave money to,

00:09:22.240 --> 00:09:24.440
was murdered the day before yesterday.

00:09:33.800 --> 00:09:34.530
This person,

00:09:36.280 --> 00:09:37.210
it's you, right?

00:09:37.920 --> 00:09:38.680
Is it you?

00:09:39.280 --> 00:09:40.040
Is it you?

00:09:40.040 --> 00:09:40.720
Don't.

00:09:40.720 --> 00:09:41.640
Don't scream.

00:09:41.640 --> 00:09:42.000
Look.

00:09:42.080 --> 00:09:42.740
Take a look.

00:09:58.160 --> 00:09:58.440
No,

00:09:58.440 --> 00:09:58.920
what do

00:09:59.440 --> 00:10:00.240
you two mean?

00:10:00.640 --> 00:10:01.970
Do you mean in the photo,

00:10:02.360 --> 00:10:02.920
only

00:10:02.920 --> 00:10:04.380
I'm the only one alive now?

00:10:05.440 --> 00:10:06.840
I'm in danger, officers.

00:10:07.320 --> 00:10:07.800
Ah,

00:10:08.640 --> 00:10:10.720
you need to send someone to protect me.

00:10:10.720 --> 00:10:11.080
No.

00:10:11.200 --> 00:10:12.040
You,

00:10:12.040 --> 00:10:12.600
what do you two mean?

00:10:12.600 --> 00:10:13.760
Do you suspect me?

00:10:13.840 --> 00:10:14.900
That I killed them?

00:10:14.960 --> 00:10:15.560
Officers,

00:10:15.560 --> 00:10:17.040
you overestimate me.

00:10:17.200 --> 00:10:18.400
Overestimate me.

00:10:18.400 --> 00:10:19.360
Do I have the guts?

00:10:19.360 --> 00:10:20.440
Do I have the ability?

00:10:20.440 --> 00:10:21.300
Let me tell you,

00:10:21.800 --> 00:10:23.730
there must be a misunderstanding.

00:10:24.720 --> 00:10:25.120
You,

00:10:25.480 --> 00:10:26.410
take a good look.

00:10:27.000 --> 00:10:28.200
You must know the girl

00:10:28.600 --> 00:10:29.730
on the coffee table.

00:10:32.720 --> 00:10:33.240
No.

00:10:34.240 --> 00:10:35.570
I didn't look carefully

00:10:35.920 --> 00:10:36.600
just now.

00:10:36.840 --> 00:10:37.320
It's fine.

00:10:37.320 --> 00:10:37.800
I don't.

00:10:38.000 --> 00:10:38.800
Look at it now.

00:10:44.440 --> 00:10:45.570
You are in this photo

00:10:45.800 --> 00:10:47.320
together,

00:10:48.800 --> 00:10:50.200
and now you are telling me

00:10:50.680 --> 00:10:51.740
you don't know her?

00:10:53.640 --> 00:10:54.200
Officer,

00:10:54.200 --> 00:10:55.440
isn't this normal?

00:10:55.880 --> 00:10:57.010
I was rich back then,

00:10:57.160 --> 00:10:57.560
right?

00:10:57.640 --> 00:10:58.840
I changed girls every day.

00:10:58.840 --> 00:10:59.760
No,

00:10:59.760 --> 00:11:00.520
not girls.

00:11:00.680 --> 00:11:03.200
I hung out with different friends every day.

00:11:03.440 --> 00:11:04.440
There were so many people.

00:11:04.440 --> 00:11:05.320
Who could see who?

00:11:05.320 --> 00:11:06.400
Would I notice her?

00:11:06.440 --> 00:11:07.160
When was

00:11:08.040 --> 00:11:08.880
that?

00:11:10.680 --> 00:11:11.840
2004 or 2005.

00:11:13.480 --> 00:11:14.740
Right before I went in.

00:11:15.520 --> 00:11:15.840
Right,

00:11:15.840 --> 00:11:16.520
it was all

00:11:16.960 --> 00:11:17.520
A Biao

00:11:17.560 --> 00:11:18.490
who arranged it.

00:11:18.680 --> 00:11:20.280
Friends with similar interests

00:11:20.280 --> 00:11:21.040
gathered together,

00:11:21.040 --> 00:11:22.300
right? Just going out.

00:11:22.560 --> 00:11:23.160
Observing and learning,

00:11:23.160 --> 00:11:23.720
exchanging feelings,

00:11:23.720 --> 00:11:24.440
looking to the future.

00:11:24.440 --> 00:11:25.320
Who took

00:11:26.280 --> 00:11:27.280
the photo?

00:11:27.280 --> 00:11:28.040
I really don't remember.

00:11:28.040 --> 00:11:29.900
Officer, it's been so many years.

00:11:30.080 --> 00:11:30.680
Liu Jiang.

00:11:30.920 --> 00:11:31.250
What?

00:11:31.720 --> 00:11:32.600
What's the matter?

00:11:32.600 --> 00:11:34.160
You really don't want the chance I gave you, do you?

00:11:34.160 --> 00:11:35.220
Isn't this normal?

00:11:35.240 --> 00:11:35.760
Officer.

00:11:35.760 --> 00:11:36.720
Who takes photos in a place like this?

00:11:36.720 --> 00:11:37.400
Let me ask you,

00:11:37.400 --> 00:11:38.640
would you take photos if you went there for fun?

00:11:38.640 --> 00:11:40.800
Wouldn't that leave evidence against yourself?

00:11:40.800 --> 00:11:41.800
Secretly filmed.

00:11:42.240 --> 00:11:44.170
It must have been secretly filmed.

00:11:45.000 --> 00:11:45.930
Go investigate.

00:11:46.160 --> 00:11:47.280
It has nothing to do with me.

00:11:47.280 --> 00:11:47.920
Liu Jiang,

00:11:48.600 --> 00:11:49.930
you just said something

00:11:50.200 --> 00:11:51.600
that makes a lot of sense.

00:11:51.960 --> 00:11:53.620
Of all the people in the photo,

00:11:54.120 --> 00:11:55.180
besides this girl,

00:11:57.080 --> 00:11:58.600
you are the only one still alive.

00:11:58.600 --> 00:11:59.080
So,

00:11:59.440 --> 00:12:01.440
do you think your current situation

00:12:01.760 --> 00:12:02.640
is dangerous?

00:12:07.200 --> 00:12:08.530
Listen to me, Liu Jiang.

00:12:09.360 --> 00:12:10.240
You already understand

00:12:10.240 --> 00:12:11.570
the current situation.

00:12:12.160 --> 00:12:13.880
The reason we're telling you so much

00:12:13.880 --> 00:12:15.040
is to protect you.

00:12:15.960 --> 00:12:16.920
But you

00:12:18.600 --> 00:12:20.860
must also give us a reason to protect you.

00:12:22.400 --> 00:12:24.460
Take another careful look this time.

00:12:28.440 --> 00:12:29.280
I'm thirsty.

00:12:30.720 --> 00:12:31.520
Oh.

00:12:32.440 --> 00:12:32.920
Caicai.

00:12:33.280 --> 00:12:34.680
Huh?

00:12:35.320 --> 00:12:35.960
Hey.

00:12:36.360 --> 00:12:37.220
This is for you,

00:12:37.520 --> 00:12:38.840
a little purple princess.

00:12:38.840 --> 00:12:40.000
Daddy doesn't know her name either,

00:12:40.000 --> 00:12:41.240
but I think she looks

00:12:41.320 --> 00:12:42.400
exactly like you.

00:12:42.480 --> 00:12:42.960
Right?

00:12:43.040 --> 00:12:44.970
Come here, let Daddy give you a hug.

00:12:45.680 --> 00:12:47.280
Look at you,

00:12:47.360 --> 00:12:48.240
buying dolls all day.

00:12:48.240 --> 00:12:49.320
There's no room at home.

00:12:49.320 --> 00:12:50.000
What a waste of money.

00:12:50.000 --> 00:12:51.040
So what?

00:12:51.080 --> 00:12:53.000
Money is meant to make Caicai happy.

00:12:53.000 --> 00:12:54.000
As long as you like it,

00:12:54.000 --> 00:12:55.880
Daddy will buy you a different doll every day.

00:12:55.880 --> 00:12:56.840
Red, orange, yellow, green, blue, indigo, purple.

00:12:56.840 --> 00:12:57.720
I'll buy them all for you, okay?

00:12:57.720 --> 00:12:58.160
Okay.

00:12:58.760 --> 00:12:59.200
Daddy,

00:12:59.200 --> 00:13:01.760
I made this at kindergarten today.

00:13:02.080 --> 00:13:02.720
Oh.

00:13:02.720 --> 00:13:03.360
Is this...

00:13:03.360 --> 00:13:04.360
Did you make this?

00:13:05.040 --> 00:13:05.840
By yourself?

00:13:07.520 --> 00:13:08.520
Aww.

00:13:09.560 --> 00:13:11.280
Daddy loves it so much.

00:13:11.600 --> 00:13:12.530
Give Daddy a hug.

00:13:12.840 --> 00:13:13.360
Oh,

00:13:13.400 --> 00:13:15.040
thank you, Caicai.

00:13:17.680 --> 00:13:19.080
Caicai, listen to Daddy.

00:13:20.480 --> 00:13:22.610
If one day Daddy isn't around anymore,

00:13:22.920 --> 00:13:24.780
you have to listen to Mommy, okay?

00:13:25.480 --> 00:13:26.340
Promise Daddy.

00:13:26.360 --> 00:13:27.320
Okay.

00:13:28.280 --> 00:13:28.640
Let's go.

00:13:28.640 --> 00:13:29.840
Let's go home and eat.

00:13:29.960 --> 00:13:30.840
Let's go.

00:13:30.840 --> 00:13:31.320
Look.

00:13:31.400 --> 00:13:32.040
It dropped.

00:13:32.040 --> 00:13:32.520
Let's go.

00:13:32.520 --> 00:13:32.840
Let's go.

00:13:32.840 --> 00:13:33.840
Let's hold hands.

00:14:23.000 --> 00:14:23.880
You wait here.

00:14:23.960 --> 00:14:24.960
I'll go check it out.

00:14:24.960 --> 00:14:25.360
Okay.

00:15:10.560 --> 00:15:11.090
Who is it?

00:15:12.880 --> 00:15:13.940
You shouldn't have

00:15:14.240 --> 00:15:16.240
given my number to your wife.

00:15:19.280 --> 00:15:20.360
What do you mean?

00:15:22.200 --> 00:15:23.800
You asked me to meet you here.

00:15:23.920 --> 00:15:24.880
It stinks in here.

00:15:24.880 --> 00:15:25.560
With the crap you've done,

00:15:25.560 --> 00:15:26.560
just stay inside.

00:15:26.800 --> 00:15:28.680
I thought about having my wife call you.

00:15:28.680 --> 00:15:29.920
But the cops are watching me.

00:15:29.920 --> 00:15:30.850
I'm telling you.

00:15:30.960 --> 00:15:33.420
If I call you, the cops will investigate you.

00:15:35.520 --> 00:15:36.440
Don't rush me.

00:15:37.440 --> 00:15:38.700
I'm only halfway done.

00:15:39.440 --> 00:15:40.240
You ruined it.

00:15:40.360 --> 00:15:42.820
I haven't even finished using the bathroom.

00:15:42.920 --> 00:15:44.360
I'll talk to you when I get out.

00:15:44.360 --> 00:15:44.720
Hey!

00:15:47.360 --> 00:15:48.290
What do you mean?

00:15:48.840 --> 00:15:49.770
What do you mean?

00:15:50.160 --> 00:15:50.920
Open it.

00:15:51.600 --> 00:15:52.400
Open the door!

00:15:52.400 --> 00:15:54.640
If you aren't afraid of the cops outside hearing,

00:15:54.640 --> 00:15:55.500
keep knocking.

00:15:59.640 --> 00:16:00.440
Let me ask you.

00:16:01.200 --> 00:16:02.600
Who killed these people?

00:16:03.280 --> 00:16:04.680
How should I know?

00:16:04.880 --> 00:16:05.940
Could it be because

00:16:07.840 --> 00:16:08.920
of what happened back then?

00:16:08.920 --> 00:16:10.200
You were the one who handled it.

00:16:10.200 --> 00:16:11.680
You said you handled it cleanly.

00:16:11.680 --> 00:16:12.600
Absolutely clean.

00:16:12.600 --> 00:16:14.460
I handled it absolutely cleanly.

00:16:14.920 --> 00:16:16.000
What exactly is going on?

00:16:16.000 --> 00:16:17.280
Bothering me every day.

00:16:17.280 --> 00:16:19.200
Are you hiding something from me?

00:16:28.160 --> 00:16:28.840
I think

00:16:29.600 --> 00:16:30.120
right now,

00:16:30.120 --> 00:16:31.360
it's quite dangerous.

00:16:31.360 --> 00:16:32.280
I think we

00:16:33.080 --> 00:16:34.400
should go lay low

00:16:35.160 --> 00:16:36.160
to avoid the risk.

00:16:36.480 --> 00:16:37.160
Back then,

00:16:37.800 --> 00:16:39.640
you had the money to fund the cripple.

00:16:39.640 --> 00:16:40.360
So could you

00:16:40.360 --> 00:16:41.690
spare a little to fund me

00:16:42.200 --> 00:16:42.960
now?

00:16:45.880 --> 00:16:46.560
Let go of me.

00:16:49.240 --> 00:16:50.600
The cripple dared to steal from me

00:16:50.600 --> 00:16:52.200
and ask for money through you

00:16:52.280 --> 00:16:53.520
because back then...

00:16:53.840 --> 00:16:55.370
Someone testified for him.

00:16:56.880 --> 00:16:57.760
What about now?

00:16:59.840 --> 00:17:00.840
Who else?

00:17:04.599 --> 00:17:05.359
Oh.

00:17:06.800 --> 00:17:07.730
You killed them.

00:17:08.760 --> 00:17:10.079
Now you want to kill me.

00:17:10.400 --> 00:17:11.660
If I wanted to kill you,

00:17:11.960 --> 00:17:13.819
it wouldn't be this much trouble.

00:17:15.240 --> 00:17:16.040
Oh my god.

00:17:21.079 --> 00:17:22.319
Liu Jiang.

00:17:23.200 --> 00:17:24.400
You have to remember,

00:17:25.560 --> 00:17:28.359
you have a wife and kids.

00:17:29.160 --> 00:17:30.200
Now,

00:17:30.520 --> 00:17:32.120
we must keep our mouths shut.

00:17:33.320 --> 00:17:34.560
Except for us,

00:17:36.160 --> 00:17:38.280
no one else can bring that up.

00:17:43.720 --> 00:17:44.980
Go hide out for a while.

00:17:45.000 --> 00:17:46.160
After things cool down,

00:17:46.160 --> 00:17:47.160
you can come back.

00:17:52.920 --> 00:17:53.520
Don't go.

00:17:54.920 --> 00:17:55.520
Don't go.